  "lore": "The Scorpius was a pattern of armoured vehicle that had entered service during the Great Crusade, having been created at the behest of the Space Wolves Legion to provide indirect fire support for assault actions via its advanced missile launcher systems. Fighting alongside Legion Predators, with which it shares many common armour and drive systems, the Scorpius proved itself well-suited to such high intensity operations and had been approved for service across the entire Legiones Astartes before the outbreak of the Horus Heresy.",
